name: The Expected
description:
I used to be a believer of extra-terrestrial creature and flying saucer. It was quite disturbing for my mind to process that there are no other being in  this fast universe. Meanwhile, I was a kid grown up in Christian family and there are not a single Bible verse mentioning about alien. But the people of today, they are undecided. 

Humans are afraid and playing oblivion. 

There are things that ever closer. 

And they are expected.
